description:
~~~ The most exciting darts game in the app store! ~~~
~~~ Helps develop your little ones’ fine motor skills ~~~

Improve your little ones’ fine motor skills daily as they practice their sniper and aiming skills!
Drag your finger up, left, right on the screen to throw darts at the flying balloons. Hit as many as you can to win highest score. Balloon Darts Challenge is easy to use and so much fun! 

What's Inside:
> Realistic throwing sensation
> Multi dart system allowing you to quickly throw as many darts as you want
> Multiple levels 
> 3 throwing challenges - Farm, Lake and House

Carefully designed for children, Balloon Darts Deluxe allows young children to improve their fine motor skills as they play and enjoy. 

Note: The House Challenge is completely free with all its stages/levels. The full version with all extra challenges and features and no ads is available with an easy to use in-app purchase inside the app.

No Sound?
Try Increasing the volume and check that your device is not set to “Mute”. The Mute button is located next to the volume buttons on the side of the device.

Still no sound?
On the iPad it's possible to have the side switch act as a screen rotation lock. In this case you can control sound volume by following these steps:
- Double tap the home button
- Swipe the lower bar from left to right
- Tap the speaker icon to the far left
- It should show “Mute Off” below the play button
